name: Frax from Ethereum
description: Bridged from Ethereum via https://bridge.pulsechain.com. Original Address - 0x853d955aCEf822Db058eb8505911ED77F175b99e. Frax is a new paradigm in stablecoin design, bringing together a two-token seigniorage share system, swap-based monetary policy, fully on-chain oracles, and decentralized governance alongside its fractional-algorithmic stablecoin design.
